description: Lyubov Sobol had earlier turned up at the home of an agent Alexei Navalny says helped poison him.
title: Alexei Navalny ally Lyubov Sobol 'held after raid'
title_page: Alexei Navalny ally Lyubov Sobol 'held after raid' - BBC News
maintext: It comes four days after she had gone to the home of Konstantin Kudryavtsev, a member of Russia's Federal Security Service (FSB), whom Mr Navalny had the previous week apparently tricked into divulging details of the attempt on his life.
